#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:237
msgid "Attendance log details"
msgstr "Detail log absensi"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:239
msgid ""
"Odoo records both the time and location for every check-in and check-out, "
"with fields varying by the method used. These detailed attendance logs can "
"confirm where an employee was on any given workday. This can be useful for "
"companies with hybrid working schedules, who may need to perform audits to "
"ensure proper compliance."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mencatat waktu dan lokasi untuk setiap check-in dan check-out, dengan "
"field yang bervariasi berdasarkan metode yang digunakan. Log absensi "
"terperinci ini dapat mengonfirmasi di mana seorang karyawan berada pada hari "
"kerja tertentu. Ini dapat berguna untuk perusahaan dengan jadwal kerja "
"hybrid, yang mungkin perlu melakukan audit untuk memastikan kepatuhan yang "
"tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:244
msgid "The detailed attendance log contains the following information:"
msgstr "Log absensi terperinci berisi informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:247
msgid "Main details"
msgstr "Detail utama"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:249
msgid ":guilabel:`Employee`: The name of the employee."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Employee`: Nama karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:250
msgid ":guilabel:`Check In`: The date and time the employee checked in."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Check In`: Tanggal dan waktu karyawan check in."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:251
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Check Out`: The date and time the employee checked out. This "
"**only** appears if the employee has checked out."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Check Out`: Tanggal dan waktu karyawan check out. Ini **hanya** "
"muncul jika karyawan telah check out."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:253
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Worked Time`: The total amount of time the employee logged for "
"the day, across multiple check-ins and outs, in an hour and minute format "
"(HH:MM)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Waktu Kerja`: Total waktu yang dicatat karyawan untuk hari "
"tersebut, mencakup beberapa check-in dan check-out, dalam format jam dan "
"menit (HH:MM)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:255
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Worked Extra Hours`: Unpaid overtime hours worked beyond the "
"expected working schedule (shows **only** when present for the employee)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jam Kerja Ekstra`: Jam lembur yang tidak dibayar yang dikerjakan "
"di luar jadwal kerja yang diharapkan (hanya ditampilkan **jika** ada untuk "
"karyawan tersebut)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extra Hours`: Approved overtime (the :guilabel:`Worked Time` "
"minus the approved :guilabel:`Worked Extra Hours`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jam Ekstra`: Lembur yang disetujui (:guilabel:`Waktu Kerja` "
"dikurangi :guilabel:`Jam Kerja Ekstra` yang disetujui)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:261
msgid "Check in/check out details"
msgstr "Detail check in/check out"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:263
msgid ""
"The following information appears for both the :guilabel:`Check In` "
"and :guilabel:`Check Out` sections."
msgstr ""
"Informasi berikut muncul untuk bagian :guilabel:`Check In` dan "
":guilabel:`Check Out`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:266
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mode`: Attendance submission method. Can be :ref:`Systray "
"<attendances/check-in>`, :ref:`Kiosk <attendances/kiosk-mode-entry>`, "
"or :guilabel:`Manual` entry."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mode`: Metode pengiriman absensi. Dapat berupa :ref:`Systray "
"<attendances/check-in>`, :ref:`Kiosk <attendances/kiosk-mode-entry>`, atau "
"entri :guilabel:`Manual`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:268
msgid ":guilabel:`IP Address`: The device's IP address used to log in or out."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Alamat IP`: Alamat IP perangkat yang digunakan untuk log in atau "
"log out."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:269
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Browser`: The web browser the employee used to log in or out."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Browser`: Browser web yang digunakan karyawan untuk log in atau "
"log out."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:270
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Localisation`: The city and country associated with the "
"computer's IP address."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Localisation`: Kota dan negara yang terkait dengan alamat IP "
"komputer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:271
msgid ""
":guilabel:`GPS Coordinates`: The coordinates when the user logged in or out. "
"To view the coordinates on a map, click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`View on Maps` button beneath the GPS coordinates. This "
"opens a map in a new browser tab, with the location pointed out."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Koordinat GPS`: Koordinat ketika user melakukan log in atau log "
"out. Untuk melihat koordinat pada peta, klik tombol :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Lihat di Peta` di bawah koordinat GPS. Ini akan membuka peta di "
"tab browser baru, dengan lokasi yang ditandai."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:None
msgid "The detailed information for an attendance entry."
msgstr "Informasi terperinci untuk entri absensi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:279
msgid "Attendance errors"
msgstr "Kesalahan absensi"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:281
msgid ""
"Entries that contain an error appear on the overview dashboard in red. In "
"the :icon:`fa-tasks` :guilabel:`(Gantt)` view, the entry appears with a red "
"background; in the :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(List)` view, the entry "
"text appears in red."
msgstr ""
"Entri yang mengandung kesalahan muncul di dashboard ringkasan dengan warna "
"merah. Dalam tampilan :icon:`fa-tasks` :guilabel:`(Gantt)`, entri muncul "
"dengan latar belakang merah; dalam tampilan :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`"
"(List)`, teks entri muncul dengan warna merah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:285
msgid ""
"An error occurs when an employee has checked in but not checked out within "
"24 hours, or when a single check-in period exceeds 16 hours."
msgstr ""
"Kesalahan terjadi ketika karyawan telah check in tetapi tidak check out "
"dalam waktu 24 jam, atau ketika satu periode check-in melebihi 16 jam."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:288
msgid ""
"To fix the error, the attendance entry must be modified or deleted. Click on "
"the entry to reveal a pop-up containing the details for that particular "
"entry. To modify the :guilabel:`Check In` and/or :guilabel:`Check Out` "
"information, click on the :guilabel:`Check In` or :guilabel:`Check Out` "
"field, and a calendar selector appears. Click on the desired date, then use "
"the time selector beneath the calendar to select the specific time for the "
"entry. When the information is correct, click :guilabel:`Apply.`"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbaiki kesalahan tersebut, entri absensi harus dimodifikasi atau "
"dihapus. Klik pada entri tersebut untuk menampilkan pop-up yang berisi "
"detail untuk entri tersebut. Untuk memodifikasi informasi :guilabel:`Check "
"In` dan/atau :guilabel:`Check Out`, klik pada field :guilabel:`Check In` "
"atau :guilabel:`Check Out`, dan pemilih kalender akan muncul. Klik pada "
"tanggal yang diinginkan, lalu gunakan pemilih waktu di bawah kalender untuk "
"memilih waktu spesifik untuk entri tersebut. Ketika informasi sudah benar, "
"klik :guilabel:`Terapkan.`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:295
msgid ""
"When all the information on the pop-up is correct, click :guilabel:`Save & "
"Close`. When the entry no longer has an error, the entry appears in gray "
"instead of red."
msgstr ""
"Ketika semua informasi pada pop-up sudah benar, klik :guilabel:`Simpan & "
"Tutup`. Ketika entri tidak lagi memiliki kesalahan, entri akan muncul dalam "
"warna abu-abu alih-alih merah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances.rst:298
msgid ""
"To delete an entry, click the red :guilabel:`Delete` button on the pop-up "
"window instead of making modifications to the entry."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus entri, klik tombol merah :guilabel:`Hapus` pada jendela pop-"
"up alih-alih melakukan modifikasi pada entri."

