#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:3
msgid "Batches"
msgstr "Batch"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:5
msgid ""
"Batches are used to generate multiple :doc:`payslips <payslips>` at once and "
"process them in a group, rather than create and process individual payslips. "
"This method not only helps the payroll department pay employees in less "
"time, but it also helps keep payslips organized."
msgstr ""
"Batch digunakan untuk menghasilkan beberapa :doc:`payslip <payslips>` "
"sekaligus dan memprosesnya dalam grup, daripada membuat dan memproses "
"payslip individual. Metode ini tidak hanya membantu departemen payroll "
"membayar karyawan dalam waktu yang lebih singkat, tetapi juga membantu "
"menjaga payslip tetap terorganisir."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:9
msgid ""
"Typically, a company's payroll department :ref:`creates a new batch <payroll/"
"new-batch>` for each salary structure, for every pay period (usually weekly, "
"bi-weekly, or monthly). If desired, batches can be further organized by "
"department, job position, or salary structure type."
msgstr ""
"Biasanya, departemen payroll perusahaan :ref:`membuat batch baru <payroll/"
"new-batch>` untuk setiap struktur gaji, untuk setiap periode pembayaran "
"(biasanya mingguan, dua mingguan, atau bulanan). Jika diinginkan, batch "
"dapat lebih diorganisir berdasarkan departemen, posisi pekerjaan, atau jenis "
"struktur gaji."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:13
msgid ""
"Once a batch is made, :ref:`payslips are added to the batch <payroll/add-"
"payslips>`, then the batch is processed, and employees are paid."
msgstr ""
"Setelah batch dibuat, :ref:`payslip ditambahkan ke batch <payroll/add-"
"payslips>`, kemudian batch diproses, dan karyawan dibayar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:17
msgid "View batches"
msgstr "Lihat batch"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:19
msgid ""
"To view all the batches in the database, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Payslips --> Batches` to display all payslip batches that have been "
"created. These payslip batches are displayed in a list view, by default."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua batch dalam database, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Payroll --> Payslip --> Batch` untuk menampilkan "
"semua batch payslip yang telah dibuat. Batch payslip ini ditampilkan dalam "
"tampilan daftar, secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:23
msgid ""
"Each batch displays the :guilabel:`Name`, the dates the batch includes "
"(the :guilabel:`Date From` and :guilabel:`Date To` fields), "
"its :guilabel:`Status`, the number of payslips in the batch "
"(:guilabel:`Payslips Count`), and the :guilabel:`Company`."
msgstr ""
"Setiap batch menampilkan :guilabel:`Nama`, tanggal yang disertakan batch "
"(kolom :guilabel:`Tanggal Dari` dan :guilabel:`Tanggal Ke`), "
":guilabel:`Status`-nya, jumlah payslip dalam batch (:guilabel:`Jumlah "
"Payslip`), dan :guilabel:`Perusahaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:None
msgid "View displaying all batches created."
msgstr "Tampilan yang menampilkan semua batch yang dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:33
msgid "Create a new batch"
msgstr "Buat batch baru"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:35
msgid ""
"New batches of payslips must be created from the :guilabel:`Payslips "
"Batches` dashboard, by navigating to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Payslips --> Batches`. Click the :guilabel:`New` button in the top-left "
"corner. Doing so reveals a blank payslip batch form on a separate page."
msgstr ""
"Batch payslip baru harus dibuat dari dashboard :guilabel:`Batch Payslip`, "
"dengan menavigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Payroll --> Payslip --> "
"Batch`. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Baru` di pojok kiri atas. Melakukan ini akan "
"menampilkan formulir batch payslip kosong pada halaman terpisah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:39
msgid ""
"On the new payslip batch form, enter the :guilabel:`Batch Name`. This should "
"be something short and descriptive, to keep records organized."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir batch payslip baru, masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Batch`. Ini harus "
"singkat dan deskriptif, untuk menjaga catatan tetap terorganisir."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:43
msgid ""
"A company pays its employees on a bi-weekly basis, and creates separate "
"batches for their two different :ref:`salary structures <payroll/structure-"
"types>` they use: worker pay and regular pay."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan membayar karyawannya secara dua mingguan, dan membuat "
"batch terpisah untuk dua :ref:`struktur gaji <payroll/structure-types>` "
"berbeda yang mereka gunakan: gaji pekerja dan gaji reguler."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:47
msgid "The names for their four August 2025 batches are:"
msgstr "Nama untuk empat batch Agustus 2025 mereka adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:49
msgid "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Worker`"
msgstr "`1-14 Agu 2025 - Pekerja`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:50
msgid "`Aug 1-14 2025 - Regular`"
msgstr "`1-14 Agu 2025 - Reguler`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:51
msgid "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Worker`"
msgstr "`15-31 Agu 2025 - Pekerja`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:52
msgid "`Aug 15-31 2025 - Regular`"
msgstr "`15-31 Agu 2025 - Reguler`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:54
msgid ""
"Next, select the date range to which the batch applies. Click into one of "
"the :guilabel:`Period` fields, and a calendar pop-up window appears. From "
"this calendar pop-up window, navigate to the correct month, and click on the "
"corresponding day for both the start and end dates of the batch."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pilih rentang tanggal di mana batch berlaku. Klik ke salah satu "
"field :guilabel:`Period`, dan jendela pop-up kalender akan muncul. Dari "
"jendela pop-up kalender ini, navigasikan ke bulan yang benar, dan klik pada "
"hari yang sesuai untuk tanggal mulai dan tanggal akhir batch."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:58
msgid ""
"The current company populates the :guilabel:`Company` field. If operating in "
"a multi-company environment, it is **not** possible to modify "
"the :guilabel:`Company` from the form. The batch **must** be created while "
"in the database for the desired company."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan saat ini mengisi field :guilabel:`Company`. Jika beroperasi di "
"lingkungan multi-perusahaan, **tidak** memungkinkan untuk mengubah "
":guilabel:`Company` dari formulir. Batch **harus** dibuat saat berada di "
"database untuk perusahaan yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:None
msgid "The details entered for the new batch."
msgstr "Rincian yang dimasukkan untuk batch baru."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:68
msgid "Add payslips to a batch"
msgstr "Tambahkan slip gaji ke batch"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:70
msgid ""
"Once a :ref:`batch has been created <payroll/new-batch>`, payslips need to "
"be added to the batch. Payslips can either be :ref:`created and added "
"<payroll/generate>` to the batch, or if they have *already* been created, "
"they can be :ref:`added to the batch <payroll/add>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah :ref:`batch dibuat <payroll/new-batch>`, slip gaji perlu ditambahkan "
"ke batch. Slip gaji dapat :ref:`dibuat dan ditambahkan <payroll/generate>` "
"ke batch, atau jika sudah dibuat sebelumnya, slip gaji dapat "
":ref:`ditambahkan ke batch <payroll/add>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:75
msgid ""
"Batches can only have payslips added to them when they are in "
"the :guilabel:`New` stage. Payslips can either be :ref:`created by the "
"database <payroll/generate>` and added to the batch, or :ref:`pre-existing "
"payslips can be individually added <payroll/add>` to the batch."
msgstr ""
"Batch hanya dapat ditambahkan slip gaji ketika berada dalam tahap "
":guilabel:`Baru`. Slip gaji dapat :ref:`dibuat oleh database <payroll/"
"generate>` dan ditambahkan ke batch, atau :ref:`slip gaji yang sudah ada "
"dapat ditambahkan secara individual <payroll/add>` ke batch."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:79
msgid ""
"Once either of these methods has been used, the status of the batch changes "
"to :guilabel:`Confirmed`, and both options to add payslips no longer appears."
msgstr ""
"Setelah salah satu metode ini digunakan, status batch berubah menjadi "
":guilabel:`Dikonfirmasi`, dan kedua opsi untuk menambahkan slip gaji tidak "
"lagi muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:85
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:102
msgid "Generate payslips"
msgstr "Buat payslip"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:87
msgid ""
"To generate the payslips and add them to the batch, first open the batch by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Batches`, and "
"click on the desired batch. Next, click the :guilabel:`Generate Payslips` "
"button and a :guilabel:`Generate Payslips` pop-up window loads."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghasilkan slip gaji dan menambahkannya ke batch, pertama buka batch "
"dengan menavigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Payroll --> Slip Gaji --> "
"Batch`, dan klik batch yang diinginkan. Selanjutnya, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Hasilkan Slip Gaji` dan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Hasilkan Slip "
"Gaji` akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:91
msgid ""
"This form contains three sections, and the configuration of this form "
"determines which payslips are created. The :guilabel:`Employees Selection` "
"section determines which employees' payslips to create. Using the drop-down "
"menus, configure the :guilabel:`Department`, :guilabel:`Job Position`, "
"and :guilabel:`Salary Structure Type` fields, if desired. As selections are "
"made, the :guilabel:`Employees` section at the bottom updates to show which "
"payslips are going to be generated."
msgstr ""
"Formulir ini berisi tiga bagian, dan konfigurasi formulir ini menentukan "
"slip gaji mana yang akan dibuat. Bagian :guilabel:`Pemilihan Karyawan` "
"menentukan slip gaji karyawan mana yang akan dibuat. Menggunakan menu drop-"
"down, konfigurasikan bidang :guilabel:`Departemen`, :guilabel:`Posisi "
"Pekerjaan`, dan :guilabel:`Jenis Struktur Gaji`, jika diinginkan. Saat "
"pilihan dibuat, bagian :guilabel:`Karyawan` di bagian bawah akan diperbarui "
"untuk menampilkan slip gaji mana yang akan dihasilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:98
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Payslip Generation` section allows the user to pick a "
"specific :guilabel:`Salary Structure` to create payslips for. If left blank, "
"the default structure for each employee is used to calculate their pay."
msgstr ""
"Bagian :guilabel:`Pembuatan Slip Gaji` memungkinkan user untuk memilih "
":guilabel:`Struktur Gaji` tertentu untuk membuat slip gaji. Jika dibiarkan "
"kosong, struktur default untuk setiap karyawan digunakan untuk menghitung "
"gaji mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:103
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo lists all employees in the :guilabel:`Employees` section "
"when generating payslips."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, Odoo mencantumkan semua karyawan dalam bagian "
":guilabel:`Karyawan` saat menghasilkan slip gaji."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:106
msgid "The list filters automatically as selections are made."
msgstr "Daftar secara otomatis difilter saat pilihan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:108
msgid ""
"Configuration is optional unless a batch is being created **excluding** "
"certain employees."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi bersifat opsional kecuali batch dibuat dengan **mengecualikan** "
"karyawan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:110
msgid ""
"Once all the desired configurations have been made, click "
"the :guilabel:`Generate` button, and all payslips are created and attached "
"to the batch. Once generated, a :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Payslips` smart "
"button appears at the top, along with the number of payslips in the batch. "
"Click this smart button to view a list of all the payslips in the batch."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua konfigurasi yang diinginkan dibuat, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Hasilkan`, dan semua slip gaji dibuat dan dilampirkan ke batch. "
"Setelah dihasilkan, tombol pintar :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Slip Gaji` "
"muncul di bagian atas, bersama dengan jumlah slip gaji dalam batch. Klik "
"tombol pintar ini untuk melihat daftar semua slip gaji dalam batch."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:115
msgid ""
"Once the payslips have been generated and attached to the batch, the status "
"of the batch changes to :guilabel:`Confirmed`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah slip gaji dihasilkan dan dilampirkan ke batch, status batch berubah "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Dikonfirmasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:None
msgid "Payslips being generated for marketing and community managers."
msgstr "Slip gaji yang dihasilkan untuk manajer pemasaran dan komunitas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:124
msgid "Add payslips"
msgstr "Tambahkan payslip"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:126
msgid ""
"Instead of generating payslips, :ref:`individual payslips that have already "
"been created <payroll/new-payslip>` can be added to a  batch. Start by "
"opening the desired batch by navigating to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Payslips --> Batches`, and clicking on the desired batch."
msgstr ""
"Alih-alih menghasilkan slip gaji, :ref:`slip gaji individual yang telah "
"dibuat <payroll/new-payslip>` dapat ditambahkan ke batch. Mulai dengan "
"membuka batch yang diinginkan dengan menavigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Payroll --> Slip Gaji --> Batch`, dan klik batch yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:130
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Add Payslips` button, and an :guilabel:`Add "
"Payslips` form loads in a pop-up window. All available payslips that have "
"not yet been added to a batch, appear on the list."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Tambahkan Slip Gaji`, dan formulir "
":guilabel:`Tambahkan Slip Gaji` akan muncul dalam jendela pop-up. Semua slip "
"gaji yang tersedia yang belum ditambahkan ke batch, muncul dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:134
msgid ""
"**All** payslips not yet assigned to a batch appear in the list, regardless "
"of status (:guilabel:`Draft`, :guilabel:`Waiting`, :guilabel:`Paid`, "
"or :guilabel:`Cancelled`). This allows already processed or cancelled "
"payslips to be grouped retroactively for reporting or record keeping "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"**Semua** slip gaji yang belum ditetapkan ke batch muncul dalam daftar, "
"terlepas dari statusnya (:guilabel:`Draft`, :guilabel:`Menunggu`, "
":guilabel:`Dibayar`, atau :guilabel:`Dibatalkan`). Ini memungkinkan slip "
"gaji yang sudah diproses atau dibatalkan untuk dikelompokkan secara "
"retroaktif untuk tujuan pelaporan atau pencatatan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:139
msgid ""
"Tick the checkbox next to each desired payslip to be added, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Select` button at the bottom. All selected payslips are added "
"to the batch, and the status of the batch changes to :guilabel:`Confirmed`. "
"A :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Payslips` smart button appears at the top, "
"along with the number of payslips in the batch. Click this smart button to "
"view a list of all the payslips in the batch."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak centang di samping setiap slip gaji yang diinginkan untuk "
"ditambahkan, lalu klik tombol :guilabel:`Pilih` di bagian bawah. Semua slip "
"gaji yang dipilih ditambahkan ke batch, dan status batch berubah menjadi "
":guilabel:`Dikonfirmasi`. Tombol pintar :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Slip "
"Gaji` muncul di bagian atas, bersama dengan jumlah slip gaji dalam batch. "
"Klik tombol pintar ini untuk melihat daftar semua slip gaji dalam batch."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:None
msgid "Adding individual payslips to a batch by selecting them form this list."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan slip gaji individual ke batch dengan memilihnya dari daftar ini."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:151
msgid "Process a batch"
msgstr "Proses batch"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:153
msgid ""
"After a :ref:`batch has been created <payroll/new-batch>` , and :ref:`all "
"required payslips have been added <payroll/add-payslips>`, the batch must "
"then be processed, and employees paid."
msgstr ""
"Setelah :ref:`batch dibuat <payroll/new-batch>`, dan :ref:`semua slip gaji "
"yang diperlukan telah ditambahkan <payroll/add-payslips>`, batch kemudian "
"harus diproses, dan karyawan dibayar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:156
msgid ""
"Open the desired batch by navigating to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Payslips --> Batches`, and clicking on the desired batch. For a batch to be "
"processed, it must have a status of :guilabel:`Confirmed`. That means the "
"batch has been created and payslips have been added to them, but the "
"payslips have *not* been processed yet."
msgstr ""
"Buka batch yang diinginkan dengan menavigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Payroll --> Slip Gaji --> Batch`, dan klik batch yang diinginkan. Agar batch "
"dapat diproses, batch harus memiliki status :guilabel:`Dikonfirmasi`. Itu "
"berarti batch telah dibuat dan slip gaji telah ditambahkan ke dalamnya, "
"tetapi slip gaji belum diproses."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:161
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Create Draft Entry` button to confirm and create a "
"draft of the individual payslips. After this occurs, the batch status "
"changes to :guilabel:`Done`."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`Create Draft Entry` untuk mengonfirmasi dan membuat "
"draft slip gaji individual. Setelah ini terjadi, status batch berubah "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Done`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:165
msgid ""
"At any time, the batch needs to be reverted back to a status "
"of :guilabel:`New`, click the :guilabel:`Set to Draft` button. This action "
"does **not** remove any payslips that have already been added to the batch, "
"instead, the status changes back to :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Kapan saja, jika batch perlu dikembalikan ke status :guilabel:`New`, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Set to Draft`. Tindakan ini **tidak** menghapus slip gaji "
"apa pun yang sudah ditambahkan ke batch, namun status berubah kembali "
"menjadi :guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:169
msgid ""
"After any desired changes have been made, click :guilabel:`Confirm` and the "
"batch status changes to :guilabel:`Confirmed`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah perubahan yang diinginkan telah dilakukan, klik :guilabel:`Confirm` "
"dan status batch berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Confirmed`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:172
msgid ""
"It is important to note, that if any payslips in the batch have a status "
"of :guilabel:`Paid`, the batch **cannot** revert to a status "
"of :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Penting untuk dicatat, bahwa jika ada slip gaji dalam batch yang memiliki "
"status :guilabel:`Paid`, batch **tidak dapat** dikembalikan ke status "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:175
msgid ""
"Once the status has changed to :guilabel:`Done`, the payments must be logged "
"in the database. Click the :guilabel:`Create Payment Report` button, and a "
"pop-up window loads, where the payment report details are entered."
msgstr ""
"Setelah status berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Done`, pembayaran harus dicatat di "
"database. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Create Payment Report`, dan jendela pop-up "
"akan muncul, di mana detail laporan pembayaran dimasukkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:179
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the :guilabel:`Export Format` for the "
"payment report. The two default options available are :guilabel:`NACHA`, "
"and :guilabel:`CSV`."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih :guilabel:`Export Format` untuk laporan "
"pembayaran. Dua opsi default yang tersedia adalah :guilabel:`NACHA`, dan "
":guilabel:`CSV`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:182
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`NACHA` option creates a compatible ACH file which is sent to "
"the company's bank, and outlines all the banking information to transfer "
"money from the company to the employees, either via direct deposit (most "
"common) or a check. Refer to the :ref:`fiscal localization document <l10n_us/"
"nacha>` for more information."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`NACHA` membuat file ACH yang kompatibel yang dikirim ke bank "
"perusahaan, dan menguraikan semua informasi perbankan untuk mentransfer uang "
"dari perusahaan ke karyawan, baik melalui setoran langsung (paling umum) "
"atau cek. Lihat :ref:`fiscal localization document <l10n_us/nacha>` untuk "
"informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:188
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payslips.rst:222
msgid ""
"Other options may be available depending on the :doc:`payroll localization "
"<payroll_localizations>` installed in the database."
msgstr ""
"Opsi lain mungkin tersedia tergantung pada :doc:`lokalisasi payroll "
"<payroll_localizations>` yang dipasang di database."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:191
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`CSV` is selected, all other fields are hidden form view. Once "
"this is selected, click the :guilabel:`Generate` button to create the "
"payment report."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`CSV` dipilih, semua field lainnya disembunyikan dari "
"tampilan. Setelah ini dipilih, klik tombol :guilabel:`Generate` untuk "
"membuat laporan pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:194
msgid ""
"Next, select the desired :guilabel:`Bank Journal` the paychecks are logged "
"on. Last, using the calendar selector, set the date the paychecks are issued "
"in the :guilabel:`Effective Date` field."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pilih :guilabel:`Bank Journal` yang diinginkan tempat cek gaji "
"dicatat. Terakhir, menggunakan pemilih kalender, atur tanggal cek gaji "
"dikeluarkan di field :guilabel:`Effective Date`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:197
msgid ""
"Once the pop-up window is configured, click the :guilabel:`Generate` button, "
"and the file appears on the batch form, in a new :guilabel:`Payment Report` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Setelah jendela pop-up dikonfigurasi, klik tombol :guilabel:`Generate`, dan "
"file akan muncul pada formulir batch, di field :guilabel:`Payment Report` "
"yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/batches.rst:200
msgid ""
"After the report is created, click the :guilabel:`Mark as paid` button to "
"mark the payslips as paid in the database."
msgstr ""
"Setelah laporan dibuat, klik tombol :guilabel:`Tandai sebagai dibayar` untuk "
"menandai slip gaji sebagai dibayar di database."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:4
msgid "Commissions"
msgstr "Komisi"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:6
msgid ""
"Commissions are payments made to employees that are earned as part of their "
"salary. The payments are awarded after a sale has been made, and the amount "
"depends on how much the sale was. Typically the amount is either a "
"percentage of the sale, or a set commission based on a structure created by "
"the company."
msgstr ""
"Komisi adalah pembayaran yang diberikan kepada karyawan sebagai bagian dari "
"gaji mereka. Pembayaran diberikan setelah penjualan terjadi, dan jumlahnya "
"bergantung pada berapa besar nilai penjualan tersebut. Biasanya jumlahnya "
"berupa persentase dari penjualan, atau komisi tetap berdasarkan struktur "
"yang dibuat oleh perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:11
msgid ""
"To pay an employee a commission they earned, a separate commission paycheck "
"must be issued to the employee. In Odoo, a commission payslip is referred to "
"as a *warrant payslip*."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membayar komisi yang diperoleh karyawan, slip gaji komisi terpisah "
"harus diterbitkan untuk karyawan tersebut. Di Odoo, slip gaji komisi disebut "
"sebagai *slip gaji waran*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:15
msgid "Create warrant payslips"
msgstr "Buat slip gaji waran"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:17
msgid ""
"Warrant payslips are generated directly from the :guilabel:`Payslips "
"Batches` dashboard, which is accessed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Batches`."
msgstr ""
"Slip gaji waran dibuat langsung dari dashboard :guilabel:`Batch Slip Gaji`, "
"yang diakses dengan menavigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Payroll --> Slip "
"Gaji --> Batch`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:20
msgid ""
"First, click the :guilabel:`Generate Warrant Payslips` button in the top-"
"left corner. Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Generate Warrant Payslips` pop-up "
"window, in which the necessary information **must** be filled out."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat Slip Gaji Waran` di pojok kiri atas. "
"Ini akan memunculkan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Buat Slip Gaji Waran`, di "
"mana informasi yang diperlukan **harus** diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:24
msgid ""
"Set the time frame the commission was earned, in the two fields next "
"to :guilabel:`Period`. Click into each field, and a calendar pop-up window "
"loads. Navigate to the desired date and click on it to select it."
msgstr ""
"Atur jangka waktu ketika komisi diperoleh, pada dua bidang di sebelah "
":guilabel:`Periode`. Klik ke setiap bidang, dan jendela pop-up kalender akan "
"dimuat. Navigasi ke tanggal yang diinginkan dan klik untuk memilihnya."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:28
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the :guilabel:`Department` in the "
"corresponding field. When a department is selected, the employees listed for "
"that department appear in the :guilabel:`Employee` section, below."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih :guilabel:`Departemen` pada bidang yang "
"sesuai. Ketika departemen dipilih, karyawan yang terdaftar untuk departemen "
"tersebut muncul di bagian :guilabel:`Karyawan`, di bawah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:32
msgid ""
"If a file is needed for the record, upload a file to the :guilabel:`Import "
"File` field, such as a sales invoice, using the :guilabel:`Upload your file` "
"button. Any file type is accepted."
msgstr ""
"Jika file diperlukan untuk catatan, unggah file ke bidang :guilabel:`Impor "
"File`, seperti faktur penjualan, menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Unggah file "
"Anda`. Semua jenis file diterima."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:35
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Employee` section, enter the "
"individual :guilabel:`Commission Amount` for each employee in the far-right "
"column. To remove an employee, click the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon to remove the line."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Karyawan`, masukkan :guilabel:`Jumlah Komisi` "
"individual untuk setiap karyawan di kolom paling kanan. Untuk menghapus "
"karyawan, klik ikon :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(tempat sampah)` untuk "
"menghapus baris."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:39
msgid ""
"Add a new commission by clicking :guilabel:`Add a Line`, and entering "
"the :guilabel:`Employee` and the appropriate :guilabel:`Commission Amount`."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan komisi baru dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Tambah Baris`, dan masukkan "
":guilabel:`Karyawan` dan :guilabel:`Jumlah Komisi` yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:42
msgid ""
"Once all the commissions are properly entered, click the :guilabel:`Generate "
"Payslips` button to create the warrant payslips in a batch, or "
"click :guilabel:`Export` to export a CSV file of the commissions."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua komisi dimasukkan dengan benar, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Generate Payslips` untuk membuat slip gaji warrant dalam batch, "
"atau klik :guilabel:`Export` untuk mengekspor file CSV dari komisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:46
msgid ""
":ref:`Process the batch <payroll/batch-process>` in the same way as a "
"typical batch to complete the payment process."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Proses batch <payroll/batch-process>` dengan cara yang sama seperti "
"batch pada umumnya untuk menyelesaikan proses pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:None
msgid "Enter the commission details."
msgstr "Masukkan detail komisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:53
msgid ":doc:`Commissions <../../sales/sales/commissions>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Commissions <../../sales/sales/commissions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:5
msgid ""
"Every employee in Odoo is required to have a running contract in order to be "
"paid. A contract outlines the terms of an employee's position, compensation, "
"working hours, and any other relevant terms."
msgstr ""
"Setiap karyawan di Odoo diharuskan memiliki kontrak yang berjalan agar dapat "
"dibayar. Kontrak menguraikan ketentuan posisi karyawan, kompensasi, jam "
"kerja, dan ketentuan relevan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:10
msgid ""
"Contract documents (PDFs) are uploaded and organized using the **Documents** "
"application, and are signed using the **Sign** application. Ensure these "
"applications are installed to send and sign contracts. Please refer to "
"the :doc:`../../productivity/documents` and :doc:`../../productivity/sign` "
"documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen kontrak (PDF) diunggah dan diatur menggunakan aplikasi **Dokumen**, "
"dan ditandatangani menggunakan aplikasi **Sign**. Pastikan aplikasi ini "
"terpasang untuk mengirim dan menandatangani kontrak. Silakan lihat "
"dokumentasi :doc:`../../productivity/documents` dan :doc:`../../productivity/"
"sign` untuk informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:18
msgid "Contracts dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard kontrak"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:20
msgid ""
"Both the **Payroll** and **Employees** apps display *identical employee "
"contract information*."
msgstr ""
"Baik aplikasi **Payroll** maupun **Karyawan** menampilkan *informasi kontrak "
"karyawan yang identik*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:22
msgid ""
"To access the contracts dashboard from the **Employees** app, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Employees app --> Employees --> Contracts`. To access the "
"contracts dashboard from the **Payroll** app, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Contracts --> Contracts`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses dashboard kontrak dari aplikasi **Karyawan**, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Employees app --> Employees --> Contracts`. Untuk mengakses "
"dashboard kontrak dari aplikasi **Payroll**, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Payroll app --> Contracts --> Contracts`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:26
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Contracts` dashboard displays all employee contracts in a "
"default list view, grouped by :guilabel:`Status`. The available status "
"groupings are :guilabel:`New`, :guilabel:`Running`, :guilabel:`Expired`, "
"and :guilabel:`Cancelled`. Each grouping displays the number of contracts "
"within the grouping."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard :guilabel:`Contracts` menampilkan semua kontrak karyawan dalam "
"tampilan daftar default, dikelompokkan berdasarkan :guilabel:`Status`. "
"Pengelompokan status yang tersedia adalah :guilabel:`New`, "
":guilabel:`Running`, :guilabel:`Expired`, dan :guilabel:`Cancelled`. Setiap "
"pengelompokan menampilkan jumlah kontrak dalam pengelompokan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Contracts dashboard view showing running contracts and contracts with issues."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan dashboard kontrak menampilkan kontrak yang berjalan dan kontrak "
"dengan masalah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:35
msgid ""
"Any changes made to contracts in the **Employees** app is reflected in the "
"**Payroll** app, and vice versa. Contract information remains identical, "
"regardless of where the contract information is accessed."
msgstr ""
"Setiap perubahan yang dilakukan pada kontrak di aplikasi **Karyawan** "
"tercermin di aplikasi **Payroll**, dan sebaliknya. Informasi kontrak tetap "
"identik, terlepas dari mana informasi kontrak diakses."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:42
msgid "Create a contract"
msgstr "Buat kontrak"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:44
msgid ""
"To create a new contract, click the :guilabel:`New` button on "
"the :ref:`Contracts dashboard <payroll/contract-dashboard>`, and a blank "
"contract form appears."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat kontrak baru, klik tombol :guilabel:`New` pada :ref:`Contracts "
"dashboard <payroll/contract-dashboard>`, dan formulir kontrak kosong akan "
"muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:50
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/work_entries.rst:252
msgid "General information section"
msgstr "Bagian informasi umum"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:52
msgid ""
"Enter the following information in the top-half of the blank contract form:"
msgstr "Masukkan informasi berikut di bagian atas formulir kontrak kosong:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contact Reference`: Type in the name or title for the contract, "
"such as `John Smith Contract`. This field is **required**."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Contact Reference`: Ketik nama atau judul untuk kontrak, seperti "
"`John Smith Contract`. Field ini **wajib**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee`: Using the drop-down menu, select the employee the "
"contract is for."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Employee`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih karyawan untuk siapa "
"kontrak ini dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Start Date`: Select the date the contract goes into "
"effect. Contracts can be created retroactively, or be created to begin at a "
"future date. The current date populates this required field by default, but "
"can be modified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Mulai Kontrak`: Pilih tanggal kontrak mulai berlaku. "
"Kontrak dapat dibuat secara retroaktif, atau dibuat untuk dimulai pada "
"tanggal mendatang. Tanggal saat ini mengisi bidang wajib ini secara default, "
"tetapi dapat dimodifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract End Date`: If the contract has a firm end date, enter "
"the date in this field. Leave this field blank if the contract runs "
"indefinitely, or until a new contract is made (when the employee has a "
"change to their job title, salary, or benefits)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Akhir Kontrak`: Jika kontrak memiliki tanggal akhir yang "
"pasti, masukkan tanggal di bidang ini. Biarkan bidang ini kosong jika "
"kontrak berjalan tanpa batas waktu, atau sampai kontrak baru dibuat (ketika "
"karyawan mengalami perubahan jabatan, gaji, atau tunjangan)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Schedule`: Select one of the available working schedules "
"the employee is expected to work, from the drop-down menu. The selected "
"working schedule determines how :doc:`work entries <work_entries>` are "
"generated, which determines the employees schedule and compensation. If this "
"field is left blank, this allows the employee to work as many or as few "
"hours as desired every week, with no restrictions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jadwal Kerja`: Pilih salah satu jadwal kerja yang tersedia yang "
"diharapkan dikerjakan oleh karyawan, dari menu drop-down. Jadwal kerja yang "
"dipilih menentukan bagaimana :doc:`entri kerja <work_entries>` dihasilkan, "
"yang menentukan jadwal dan kompensasi karyawan. Jika bidang ini dibiarkan "
"kosong, hal ini memungkinkan karyawan bekerja sebanyak atau sesedikit "
"mungkin jam yang diinginkan setiap minggu, tanpa batasan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:70
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Working Schedule` drop-down menu displays all the working "
"schedules for the selected company. To modify or add to this list, go "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Working Schedules`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New`, and create a new working schedule, or click on an "
"existing working schedule and make edits."
msgstr ""
"Menu drop-down :guilabel:`Jadwal Kerja` menampilkan semua jadwal kerja untuk "
"perusahaan yang dipilih. Untuk memodifikasi atau menambah daftar ini, buka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Payroll --> Konfigurasi --> Jadwal Kerja`. Klik "
":guilabel:`Baru`, dan buat jadwal kerja baru, atau klik jadwal kerja yang "
"ada dan buat pengeditan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:77
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Source`: Using the drop-down menu, select how "
"the :doc:`work entries <work_entries>` are generated. This field is "
"**required**. Click the radio button next to the desired selection. The "
"options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sumber Entri Kerja`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih bagaimana "
":doc:`entri kerja <work_entries>` dibuat. Kolom ini **wajib** diisi. Klik "
"tombol radio di sebelah pilihan yang diinginkan. Pilihannya adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Schedule`: Work entries are generated based on the "
"selected :guilabel:`Working Schedule`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jadwal Kerja`: Entri kerja dibuat berdasarkan :guilabel:`Jadwal "
"Kerja` yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Attendances`: Work entries are generated based on the employee's "
"check-in records in the **Attendances** app. (This requires the "
"**Attendances** app to be installed)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Absensi`: Entri kerja dibuat berdasarkan catatan check-in "
"karyawan di aplikasi **Absensi**. (Ini memerlukan aplikasi **Absensi** "
"terpasang)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Planning`: Work entries are generated based on the planned "
"schedule for the employee from the **Planning** app. (This requires the "
"**Planning** app to be installed)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perencanaan`: Entri kerja dibuat berdasarkan jadwal yang "
"direncanakan untuk karyawan dari aplikasi **Perencanaan**. (Ini memerlukan "
"aplikasi **Perencanaan** terpasang)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salary Structure Type`: Select one of the salary structure types "
"from the drop-down menu. The default salary structure types "
"are :guilabel:`Employee` or :guilabel:`Worker`. A :ref:`new salary structure "
"type <payroll/new-structure-type>` can be created, if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Struktur Gaji`: Pilih salah satu jenis struktur gaji dari "
"menu drop-down. Jenis struktur gaji default adalah :guilabel:`Karyawan` atau "
":guilabel:`Pekerja`. Sebuah :ref:`jenis struktur gaji baru <payroll/new-"
"structure-type>` dapat dibuat jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Department`: Select the department the employee is working "
"within, using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Departemen`: Pilih departemen tempat karyawan bekerja menggunakan "
"menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Job Position`: Select the employee's specific job position using "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Posisi Jabatan`: Pilih posisi jabatan spesifik karyawan "
"menggunakan menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:96
msgid ""
"If the selected :guilabel:`Job Position` has a contract template linked to "
"it with a specific :guilabel:`Salary Structure Type`, the :guilabel:`Salary "
"Structure Type` changes to the one associated with that :guilabel:`Job "
"Position`."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`Posisi Pekerjaan` yang dipilih memiliki templat kontrak yang "
"ditautkan dengan :guilabel:`Jenis Struktur Gaji` tertentu, :guilabel:`Jenis "
"Struktur Gaji` berubah menjadi yang terkait dengan :guilabel:`Posisi "
"Pekerjaan` tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select the type of "
"contract being created. The default options "
"are :guilabel:`Permanent`, :guilabel:`Temporary`, :guilabel:`Seasonal`, :guilabel:`Full-"
"Time`, :guilabel:`Intern`, :guilabel:`Student`, :guilabel:`Apprenticeship`, :guilabel:`Thesis`, :guilabel:`Statutory`, "
"and :guilabel:`Employee`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Kontrak`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih jenis kontrak "
"yang akan dibuat. Pilihan default adalah :guilabel:`Tetap`, "
":guilabel:`Sementara`, :guilabel:`Musiman`, :guilabel:`Penuh Waktu`, "
":guilabel:`Magang`, :guilabel:`Mahasiswa`, :guilabel:`Pemagangan`, "
":guilabel:`Tesis`, :guilabel:`Wajib`, dan :guilabel:`Karyawan`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage on Payroll`: Enter the employee's monthly wage in this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gaji di Payroll`: Masukkan gaji bulanan karyawan pada kolom ini."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:107
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Working Schedule` drop-down menu displays all the working "
"times for the selected :guilabel:`Company`. To modify or add to this list, "
"go to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Working Times`, and "
"either :guilabel:`Create` a new working time, or click on an existing "
"working time, then edit it by clicking :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Menu drop-down :guilabel:`Jadwal Kerja` menampilkan semua waktu kerja untuk "
":guilabel:`Perusahaan` yang dipilih. Untuk memodifikasi atau menambah daftar "
"ini, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Payroll --> Konfigurasi --> Waktu Kerja`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Buat` waktu kerja baru, atau klik waktu kerja yang ada, lalu "
"edit dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HR Responsible`: Select the person who is responsible for "
"validating the contract using the drop-down menu. This field is required."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penanggung Jawab SDM`: Pilih orang yang bertanggung jawab untuk "
"memvalidasi kontrak menggunakan menu drop-down. Kolom ini wajib diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:116
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`HR Responsible` field only appears if the  **Salary "
"Configurator** (`hr_contract_salary`) module and the **Sign** app are both "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Penanggung Jawab SDM` hanya muncul jika modul "
"**Configurator Gaji** (`hr_contract_salary`) dan aplikasi **Sign** keduanya "
"terpasang."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid "New contract form to be filled in when creating a new contract."
msgstr "Formulir kontrak baru yang harus diisi saat membuat kontrak baru."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:123
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:332
msgid "Salary information tab"
msgstr "Tab informasi gaji"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:125
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Salary Information` tab is where the specific details of how "
"much and how often the employee is paid. Fill in the following fields in "
"this tab:"
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Informasi Gaji` adalah tempat detail spesifik tentang berapa "
"banyak dan seberapa sering karyawan dibayar. Isi kolom-kolom berikut pada "
"tab ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select what kind of pay the "
"employee receives. The two default options are :guilabel:`Fixed Wage` "
"or :guilabel:`Hourly Wage`. Select :guilabel:`Fixed Wage` for salaried "
"employees, and select :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` for employees who are paid "
"based on their logged worked hours."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Gaji`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih jenis pembayaran "
"yang diterima karyawan. Dua pilihan default adalah :guilabel:`Gaji Tetap` "
"atau :guilabel:`Gaji Per Jam`. Pilih :guilabel:`Gaji Tetap` untuk karyawan "
"bergaji, dan pilih :guilabel:`Gaji Per Jam` untuk karyawan yang dibayar "
"berdasarkan jam kerja yang tercatat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule Pay`: Using the drop-down menu, select how often the "
"employee is paid. The default options "
"are :guilabel:`Annually`, :guilabel:`Semi-"
"annually`, :guilabel:`Quarterly`, :guilabel:`Bi-"
"monthly`, :guilabel:`Monthly`, :guilabel:`Semi-monthly`,  :guilabel:`Bi-"
"weekly`, :guilabel:`Weekly`, or :guilabel:`Daily`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jadwal Pembayaran`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih seberapa "
"sering karyawan dibayar. Pilihan default adalah :guilabel:`Tahunan`, "
":guilabel:`Semi-tahunan`, :guilabel:`Triwulanan`, :guilabel:`Dua bulan "
"sekali`, :guilabel:`Bulanan`, :guilabel:`Semi-bulanan`, :guilabel:`Dua "
"minggu sekali`, :guilabel:`Mingguan`, atau :guilabel:`Harian`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage`: Enter the amount the employee receives each pay period. "
"The first field allows for a wage to be entered, the second field displays "
"how often the pay is issued to the employee. The second field *cannot* be "
"modified, and is updated when the :guilabel:`Schedule Pay` field changes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Upah`: Masukkan jumlah yang diterima karyawan setiap periode "
"pembayaran. Bidang pertama memungkinkan upah dimasukkan, bidang kedua "
"menampilkan seberapa sering pembayaran diberikan kepada karyawan. Bidang "
"kedua *tidak dapat* dimodifikasi, dan diperbarui ketika bidang "
":guilabel:`Jadwal Bayar` berubah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)`: This field automatically updates after "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule Pay` and :guilabel:`Wage` fields are entered. This "
"amount is the total yearly cost for the employer. This field can be "
"modified. However, if this is modified, the :guilabel:`Wage` field updates, "
"accordingly. Ensure both the :guilabel:`Wage` and :guilabel:`Yearly Cost "
"(Real)` are correct if this field is modified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Biaya Tahunan (Riil)`: Kolom ini secara otomatis diperbarui "
"setelah kolom :guilabel:`Jadwal Pembayaran` dan :guilabel:`Gaji` diisi. "
"Jumlah ini adalah total biaya tahunan untuk pemberi kerja. Kolom ini dapat "
"dimodifikasi. Namun, jika dimodifikasi, kolom :guilabel:`Gaji` akan "
"diperbarui sesuai. Pastikan :guilabel:`Gaji` dan :guilabel:`Biaya Tahunan "
"(Riil)` sudah benar jika kolom ini dimodifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:145
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monthly Cost (Real)`: This field automatically updates after "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule Pay` and :guilabel:`Wage` fields are entered. This "
"amount is the total monthly cost for the employer. This field **cannot** be "
"modified, and is calculated based on the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Biaya Bulanan (Riil)`: Kolom ini secara otomatis diperbarui "
"setelah kolom :guilabel:`Jadwal Pembayaran` dan :guilabel:`Gaji` diisi. "
"Jumlah ini adalah total biaya bulanan untuk pemberi kerja. Kolom ini **tidak "
"dapat** dimodifikasi, dan dihitung berdasarkan :guilabel:`Biaya Tahunan "
"(Riil)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid "The Salary Information tab filled out."
msgstr "Tab Informasi Gaji yang telah diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:154
#: ../../content/applications/hr/recruitment/add-new-applicants.rst:109
msgid "Details tab"
msgstr "Tab Detail"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:156
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Details` tab of the contract houses the contract template "
"information, accounting information (refer to the :doc:`country-specific "
"localization document <payroll_localizations>` for more information), any "
"part time work information, and notes. Fill out the following fields in this "
"tab:"
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Detail` pada kontrak memuat informasi template kontrak, "
"informasi akuntansi (lihat :doc:`dokumen lokalisasi khusus negara "
"<payroll_localizations>` untuk informasi lebih lanjut), informasi pekerjaan "
"paruh waktu, dan catatan. Isi kolom-kolom berikut pada tab ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:161
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Template`: Using the drop-down menu, select "
"a :ref:`contract template <payroll/contract-template>` to use when making an "
"offer to an applicant."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Template Kontrak`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih "
":ref:`template kontrak <payroll/contract-template>` untuk digunakan saat "
"membuat penawaran kepada pelamar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:163
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Originated Offer`: This field automatically populates with the "
"original offer sent to the employee. This field is **not** modifiable, and "
"is only populated if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penawaran Asal`: Kolom ini secara otomatis terisi dengan "
"penawaran asli yang dikirim kepada karyawan. Kolom ini **tidak dapat** "
"dimodifikasi, dan hanya terisi jika berlaku."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:165
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Part Time`: Tick the checkbox if the contract is for part time "
"work. Once enabled, a percentage field appears next to the checkbox. The "
"percentage **cannot** be modified, and automatically updates based on the "
"selected :guilabel:`Working Schedule` in the top-half of the contract, "
"compared to the typical working schedule for the company (typically 40 hours/"
"week)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Paruh Waktu`: Centang kotak jika kontrak adalah untuk pekerjaan "
"paruh waktu. Setelah diaktifkan, kolom persentase muncul di sebelah kotak "
"centang. Persentase **tidak dapat** dimodifikasi, dan secara otomatis "
"diperbarui berdasarkan :guilabel:`Jadwal Kerja` yang dipilih pada bagian "
"atas kontrak, dibandingkan dengan jadwal kerja standar untuk perusahaan "
"(biasanya 40 jam/minggu)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:171
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Standard Calendar`: This field is automatically populated with "
"the default working schedule for the company. In most cases, this "
"is :guilabel:`Standard 40 hours/week`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kalender Standar`: Kolom ini secara otomatis terisi dengan jadwal "
"kerja default untuk perusahaan. Dalam sebagian besar kasus, ini adalah "
":guilabel:`Standar 40 jam/minggu`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Part Time Work Entry Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select the "
"work entry type that generates the balance of a full-time working schedule."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Entri Kerja Paruh Waktu`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih "
"jenis entri kerja yang menghasilkan saldo jadwal kerja penuh waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:177
msgid ""
"An employee contract is being created for a part-time employee who works 20 "
"hours a week."
msgstr ""
"Kontrak karyawan sedang dibuat untuk karyawan paruh waktu yang bekerja 20 "
"jam per minggu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:179
msgid ""
"To configure this, the employee's :guilabel:`Working Schedule` is set "
"to :guilabel:`20 Hours/Part time` in the :ref:`general information section "
"<payroll/gen-info>`. In the :guilabel:`Details` tab, the :guilabel:`Part "
"Time` checkbox is ticked, and the percentage is set to `50`. "
"The :guilabel:`Standard Calendar` is set to :guilabel:`Standard 40 hours/"
"week`, and the :guilabel:`Part Time Work Entry Type` is set "
"to :guilabel:`Unpaid`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi ini, :guilabel:`Jadwal Kerja` karyawan diatur ke "
":guilabel:`20 Jam/Paruh waktu` di :ref:`bagian informasi umum <payroll/gen-"
"info>`. Di tab :guilabel:`Detail`, kotak centang :guilabel:`Paruh Waktu` "
"dicentang, dan persentase diatur ke `50`. :guilabel:`Kalender Standar` "
"diatur ke :guilabel:`Standar 40 jam/minggu`, dan :guilabel:`Jenis Entri "
"Kerja Paruh Waktu` diatur ke :guilabel:`Tidak Dibayar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:185
msgid ""
"When a typical work week is processed in the **Payroll** app, the employee "
"generates twenty (20) hours of regular work entries under the work entry "
"type `Attendance`, and another twenty (20) hours of work entries under the "
"work entry type `Unpaid`, for a total of forty (40) hours worth of work "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Ketika minggu kerja biasa diproses di aplikasi **Payroll**, karyawan "
"menghasilkan dua puluh (20) jam entri kerja reguler di bawah jenis entri "
"kerja `Kehadiran`, dan dua puluh (20) jam entri kerja lainnya di bawah jenis "
"entri kerja `Tidak Dibayar`, dengan total empat puluh (40) jam entri kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:190
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Notes`: Enter any relevant notes for the contract in this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Catatan`: Masukkan catatan yang relevan untuk kontrak di bidang "
"ini."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid "The Details tab filled out."
msgstr "Tab Detail telah diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:196
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:368
msgid "Signatories tab"
msgstr "Tab Penandatangan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:198
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Signatories` tab is where the default contract templates are "
"selected, for both new and updated contracts."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Penandatangan` adalah tempat template kontrak default "
"dipilih, baik untuk kontrak baru maupun yang diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:201
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the default contract template to use when "
"creating a new or updated contract, in the respective fields."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih template kontrak default untuk digunakan "
"saat membuat kontrak baru atau yang diperbarui, di bidang masing-masing."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:204
msgid ""
"Once a PDF template is selected, any mapped signature fields in the file "
"appear in a list, below the selection, identifying who must sign the "
"document. These fields **cannot** be updated."
msgstr ""
"Setelah template PDF dipilih, bidang tanda tangan yang dipetakan dalam file "
"akan muncul dalam daftar, di bawah pilihan, yang mengidentifikasi siapa yang "
"harus menandatangani dokumen. Bidang ini **tidak dapat** diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:207
msgid ""
"Any changes to the template and signatories but be done in the **Sign** app, "
"where contract templates are uploaded, modified, and stored."
msgstr ""
"Setiap perubahan pada template dan penandatangan harus dilakukan di aplikasi "
"**Sign**, tempat template kontrak diunggah, dimodifikasi, dan disimpan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:211
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`PDF Template` fields are only visible if the **Sign** app is "
"installed, along with the :guilabel:`hr_contract_salary` "
"and :guilabel:`hr_contract_salary_payroll` :doc:`modules <../../general/"
"apps_modules>`."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Template PDF` hanya terlihat jika aplikasi **Sign** "
"diinstal, bersama dengan :guilabel:`hr_contract_salary` dan "
":guilabel:`hr_contract_salary_payroll` :doc:`modul <../../general/"
"apps_modules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid "The Signatories tab with the roles specified for signing."
msgstr "Tab Penandatangan dengan peran yang ditentukan untuk penandatanganan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:219
msgid "Personal documents tab"
msgstr "Tab dokumen pribadi"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:221
msgid ""
"Occasionally, additional paperwork may be required when creating a contract, "
"such as legal documents declaring the employee is able to work in the "
"country. When this situation occurs, Odoo allows for one image file of the "
"necessary document to be attached to a contract in the :guilabel:`Personal "
"Documents` tab."
msgstr ""
"Terkadang, dokumen tambahan mungkin diperlukan saat membuat kontrak, seperti "
"dokumen hukum yang menyatakan karyawan dapat bekerja di negara tersebut. "
"Ketika situasi ini terjadi, Odoo memungkinkan satu file gambar dari dokumen "
"yang diperlukan untuk dilampirkan ke kontrak di tab :guilabel:`Dokumen "
"Pribadi`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:226
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Upload your file` button, navigate to the desired "
"document, and click :guilabel:`Select` to attach the file to the contract. "
"The file name appears on the :guilabel:`Image` line."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`Unggah file Anda`, arahkan ke dokumen yang "
"diinginkan, dan klik :guilabel:`Pilih` untuk melampirkan file ke kontrak. "
"Nama file akan muncul di baris :guilabel:`Gambar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:231
msgid ""
"This tab **only** appears after an :guilabel:`Employee` is selected. "
"Additionally, only image files can be attached in this field at this time."
msgstr ""
"Tab ini **hanya** muncul setelah :guilabel:`Karyawan` dipilih. Selain itu, "
"hanya file gambar yang dapat dilampirkan di bidang ini saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:235
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salary_attachments.rst:3
msgid "Salary attachments"
msgstr "Lampiran-lampiran gaji"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:237
msgid ""
"After an employee is selected for the contract, a :icon:`fa-"
"book` :guilabel:`Salary Attachments` smart button appears at the top of the "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Setelah karyawan dipilih untuk kontrak, tombol pintar :icon:`fa-book` "
":guilabel:`Lampiran Gaji` muncul di bagian atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:240
msgid ""
"For new employees who do not currently have a contract, the smart button "
"displays :guilabel:`New`. If the contract is being updated for a current "
"employee who already has salary attachments configured, the smart button "
"displays the number of salary attachments currently running."
msgstr ""
"Untuk karyawan baru yang saat ini tidak memiliki kontrak, tombol pintar "
"menampilkan :guilabel:`Baru`. Jika kontrak sedang diperbarui untuk karyawan "
"saat ini yang sudah memiliki lampiran gaji yang dikonfigurasi, tombol pintar "
"menampilkan jumlah lampiran gaji yang sedang berjalan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:244
msgid ""
":doc:`Create or update any necessary salary attachments "
"<salary_attachments>` for the contract, before sending."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Buat atau perbarui lampiran gaji yang diperlukan <salary_attachments>` "
"untuk kontrak, sebelum mengirim."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:248
msgid "Send a contract"
msgstr "Kirim kontrak"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:250
msgid ""
"After a contract has been created and configured, the next step is to send "
"it to the employee or applicant. Click the :guilabel:`Generate Offer` "
"button, and the :guilabel:`Offer for (Employee)` form loads."
msgstr ""
"Setelah kontrak dibuat dan dikonfigurasi, langkah selanjutnya adalah "
"mengirimkannya kepada karyawan atau pelamar. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat "
"Penawaran`, dan formulir :guilabel:`Penawaran untuk (Karyawan)` akan dimuat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:254
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Offer for (Employee)` form displays all the basic information "
"from the contract, as well as a link the employee can use to sign the "
"contract. The last field on the form is a :guilabel:`Validity Days Count` "
"field. This indicates how long the offer is valid. Enter the desired number "
"of days in the field. The default is `30` days."
msgstr ""
"Formulir :guilabel:`Offer for (Employee)` menampilkan semua informasi dasar "
"dari kontrak, serta tautan yang dapat digunakan karyawan untuk "
"menandatangani kontrak. Field terakhir pada formulir adalah field "
":guilabel:`Validity Days Count`. Ini menunjukkan berapa lama penawaran "
"berlaku. Masukkan jumlah hari yang diinginkan di field tersebut. Default "
"adalah `30` hari."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:259
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send By Email` and a pop-up email window loads, using a "
"preconfigured default email template. Click :guilabel:`Send` to send the "
"offer."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Send By Email` dan jendela email pop-up akan dimuat, "
"menggunakan template email default yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya. Klik "
":guilabel:`Send` untuk mengirim penawaran."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:263
msgid ""
"In order to send a contract using the :guilabel:`Generate Offer` button, "
"there **must** be an employee signature field on the contract PDF being sent."
msgstr ""
"Agar dapat mengirim kontrak menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Generate Offer`, "
"**harus** ada field tanda tangan karyawan pada PDF kontrak yang dikirim."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid "Send the contract to the employee via one of the buttons."
msgstr "Kirim kontrak ke karyawan melalui salah satu tombol."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:270
msgid "Contract status"
msgstr "Status kontrak"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:272
msgid ""
"When creating and sending out a contract, the default status of the contract "
"is :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat dan mengirim kontrak, status default kontrak adalah "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:274
msgid ""
"Once there is a minimum of one completed signature on the document, the "
"status changes to :guilabel:`Partially Signed`. Internal users, such as HR "
"and recruitment employees, are alerted in the database when there is a "
"signature requested of them."
msgstr ""
"Setelah ada minimal satu tanda tangan yang selesai pada dokumen, status "
"berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Partially Signed`. Pengguna internal, seperti "
"karyawan HR dan perekrutan, akan mendapat notifikasi di database ketika ada "
"permintaan tanda tangan dari mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:278
msgid ""
"After all required parties have signed the contract, the status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Fully Signed`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua pihak yang diperlukan telah menandatangani kontrak, status "
"berubah menjadi :guilabel:`Fully Signed`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:280
msgid "All status changes happen automatically as the document is signed."
msgstr ""
"Semua perubahan status terjadi secara otomatis saat dokumen ditandatangani."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:285
msgid "Contract templates"
msgstr "Template kontrak"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:287
msgid ""
"Contract *templates* eliminate the need to configure new contracts every "
"time an employee is hired."
msgstr ""
"*Template* kontrak menghilangkan kebutuhan untuk mengonfigurasi kontrak baru "
"setiap kali karyawan dipekerjakan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:290
msgid ""
"Having multiple contract templates allows for faster contract creation for "
"different types of employment positions that are commonly filled, such as "
"full time, part time, seasonal, etc."
msgstr ""
"Memiliki beberapa template kontrak memungkinkan pembuatan kontrak yang lebih "
"cepat untuk berbagai jenis posisi pekerjaan yang biasanya diisi, seperti "
"penuh waktu, paruh waktu, musiman, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:293
msgid ""
"Contract templates are created through the **Payroll** app configuration "
"menu, and stored in the **Documents** app."
msgstr ""
"Template kontrak dibuat melalui menu konfigurasi aplikasi **Payroll**, dan "
"disimpan di aplikasi **Dokumen**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:297
msgid ""
"To access contract templates, the **Salary Configurator** "
"(`hr_contract_salary`) module **must** be :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses template kontrak, modul **Salary Configurator** "
"(`hr_contract_salary`) **harus** :ref:`diinstal <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:300
msgid ""
"To view all contract templates, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Configuration --> Templates`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua template kontrak, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Payroll --> Konfigurasi --> Template`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:303
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Contract Templates` page lists all existing templates. Click "
"a template line to open and edit it."
msgstr ""
"Halaman :guilabel:`Template Kontrak` mencantumkan semua template yang ada. "
"Klik baris template untuk membuka dan mengeditnya."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:306
msgid ""
"To create a new contract template, click the :guilabel:`New` button. Then, "
"enter the following information on the blank contract template form that "
"appears:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat templat kontrak baru, klik tombol :guilabel:`Baru`. Kemudian, "
"masukkan informasi berikut pada formulir templat kontrak kosong yang muncul:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:309
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Reference`: Enter a brief description for the template. "
"This should be clear and easily understood, as this name appears in the "
"**Recruitment** application, as well."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Referensi Kontrak`: Masukkan deskripsi singkat untuk template. "
"Ini harus jelas dan mudah dipahami, karena nama ini muncul di aplikasi "
"**Perekrutan**, juga."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:311
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Schedule`: Select the desired working schedule the "
"contract applies to from the drop-down menu. If a new working schedule is "
"needed, create a :ref:`new working schedule <payroll/new-working-schedule>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jadwal Kerja`: Pilih jadwal kerja yang diinginkan untuk kontrak "
"ini dari menu drop-down. Jika diperlukan jadwal kerja baru, buat "
":ref:`jadwal kerja baru <payroll/new-working-schedule>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:314
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Source`: Select :ref:`how the work entries are "
"generated <payroll/work-entry-source>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sumber Entri Kerja`: Pilih :ref:`cara entri kerja dibuat <payroll/"
"work-entry-source>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:316
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salary Structure Type`: Select the :ref:`salary structure type "
"<payroll/structure-types>` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Struktur Gaji`: Pilih :ref:`jenis struktur gaji <payroll/"
"structure-types>` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:318
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Department`: Select the department the contract template applies "
"to from the drop-down menu. If blank, the template applies to all "
"departments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Department`: Pilih departemen yang berlaku untuk template kontrak "
"dari menu drop-down. Jika kosong, template berlaku untuk semua departemen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:320
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Job Position`: Select the :doc:`job position <../recruitment/"
"new_job>` the contract template applies to from the drop-down menu. If "
"blank, the template applies to all job positions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Posisi Pekerjaan`: Pilih :doc:`posisi pekerjaan <../recruitment/"
"new_job>` yang berlaku untuk template kontrak dari menu drop-down. Jika "
"kosong, template berlaku untuk semua posisi pekerjaan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:322
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Type`: Select the type of contract from the drop-down "
"menu. This list is the same as the *employment type*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Kontrak`: Pilih jenis kontrak dari menu drop-down. Daftar "
"ini sama dengan *jenis pekerjaan*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:324
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage on Payroll`: Enter the monthly wage in the field."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Gaji pada Payroll`: Masukkan gaji bulanan di kolom ini."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:325
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HR Responsible`: Select the employee responsible for validating "
"contracts, using this template, from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penanggung Jawab HR`: Pilih karyawan yang bertanggung jawab untuk "
"memvalidasi kontrak menggunakan template ini dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid "A new contract template form, with the fields filled in."
msgstr "Formulir templat kontrak baru dengan bidang yang telah diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:334
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage Type`: Select either :guilabel:`Fixed Wage` "
"or :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jenis Gaji`: Pilih :guilabel:`Gaji Tetap` atau :guilabel:`Gaji "
"Per Jam` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:336
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule Pay`: Using the drop-down menu, select how often the "
"employee is paid. Options include :guilabel:`Annually`, :guilabel:`Semi-"
"annually`, :guilabel:`Quarterly`, :guilabel:`Bi-"
"monthly`, :guilabel:`Monthly`, :guilabel:`Semi-monthly`, :guilabel:`Bi-"
"weekly`, :guilabel:`Weekly`, or :guilabel:`Daily`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jadwal Pembayaran`: Menggunakan menu drop-down, pilih seberapa "
"sering karyawan dibayar. Pilihan meliputi :guilabel:`Tahunan`, "
":guilabel:`Semesteran`, :guilabel:`Triwulanan`, :guilabel:`Dua Bulanan`, "
":guilabel:`Bulanan`, :guilabel:`Setengah Bulanan`, :guilabel:`Dua Mingguan`, "
":guilabel:`Mingguan`, atau :guilabel:`Harian`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:340
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage`: Enter the gross wage. The time period presented in this "
"field is based on what is selected for the :guilabel:`Scheduled Pay` field. "
"It is recommended to populate the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` field "
"*first*, since that entry updates this field automatically."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gaji`: Masukkan gaji kotor. Periode waktu yang ditampilkan di "
"kolom ini berdasarkan apa yang dipilih untuk kolom :guilabel:`Jadwal "
"Pembayaran`. Disarankan untuk mengisi kolom :guilabel:`Biaya Tahunan (Riil)` "
"*terlebih dahulu*, karena entri tersebut memperbarui kolom ini secara "
"otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:343
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)`: Enter the total yearly cost the employee "
"costs the employer. When this value is entered, the :guilabel:`Monthly Cost "
"(Real)` is automatically updated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Biaya Tahunan (Riil)`: Masukkan total biaya tahunan yang "
"dikeluarkan pemberi kerja untuk karyawan. Ketika nilai ini dimasukkan, "
":guilabel:`Biaya Bulanan (Riil)` akan diperbarui secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:345
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monthly Cost (Real)`: This field is **not** editable. The value "
"is automatically populated after the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` is "
"entered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Biaya Bulanan (Riil)`: Kolom ini **tidak** dapat diedit. Nilai "
"ini diisi secara otomatis setelah :guilabel:`Biaya Tahunan (Riil)` "
"dimasukkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:349
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Schedule Pay`, :guilabel:`Wage`, and :guilabel:`Yearly Cost "
"(Real)` fields are all linked. If any of these fields are updated, the other "
"two fields automatically update to reflect the change. It is best practice "
"to check these three fields if any modifications have been made, to ensure "
"they are accurate."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Jadwal Gaji`, :guilabel:`Upah`, dan :guilabel:`Biaya "
"Tahunan (Riil)` semuanya saling terkait. Jika salah satu bidang ini "
"diperbarui, dua bidang lainnya secara otomatis diperbarui untuk mencerminkan "
"perubahan tersebut. Sebaiknya periksa ketiga bidang ini jika ada modifikasi "
"yang telah dilakukan untuk memastikan akurasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:None
msgid "The salary information tab, with the fields filled in."
msgstr "Tab informasi gaji dengan bidang yang telah diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:358
msgid "Benefits and deductions"
msgstr "Tunjangan dan potongan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:360
msgid ""
"Depending on the :doc:`payroll localization <payroll_localizations>` for the "
"company, the entries presented in this section either vary, or may not "
"appear at all. For example, some entries may pertain to retirement accounts, "
"health insurance benefits, and commuter benefits."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada :doc:`lokalisasi payroll <payroll_localizations>` untuk "
"perusahaan, entri yang ditampilkan di bagian ini bervariasi, atau mungkin "
"tidak muncul sama sekali. Misalnya, beberapa entri mungkin berkaitan dengan "
"rekening pensiun, manfaat asuransi kesehatan, dan manfaat transportasi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:364
msgid ""
"Enter the monetary amounts or percentages to specify how much of the "
"employee's salary goes to the various benefits and deductions."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan jumlah uang atau persentase untuk menentukan berapa banyak gaji "
"karyawan yang dialokasikan untuk berbagai tunjangan dan potongan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:370
msgid ""
"This tab outlines which documents the employee must sign to either accept a "
"new offer or an updated contract."
msgstr ""
"Tab ini menguraikan dokumen mana yang harus ditandatangani karyawan untuk "
"menerima penawaran baru atau kontrak yang diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:373
msgid ""
":guilabel:`New Contract PDF Template`: Select the default document that a "
"new employee has to sign to accept an offer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Template PDF Kontrak Baru`: Pilih dokumen default yang harus "
"ditandatangani karyawan baru untuk menerima penawaran."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:375
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Update PDF Template`: Select the default document that a "
"current employee has to sign to update their contract."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Template PDF Pembaruan Kontrak`: Pilih dokumen default yang harus "
"ditandatangani karyawan saat ini untuk memperbarui kontrak mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:379
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/documents`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/documents`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:380
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/sign`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/sign`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:3
msgid "Headcount report"
msgstr "Laporan jumlah karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Headcount report* in the **Payroll** app shows the number of employees "
"on payroll and allows headcount comparisons between different periods of "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Laporan *Jumlah karyawan* di aplikasi **Payroll** menampilkan jumlah "
"karyawan dalam daftar gaji dan memungkinkan perbandingan jumlah karyawan "
"antara periode waktu yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:9
msgid "Create a headcount report"
msgstr "Membuat laporan jumlah karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:11
msgid ""
"Create a headcount report to see the number of employees at a specific time "
"or compare headcounts across periods."
msgstr ""
"Buat laporan jumlah karyawan untuk melihat jumlah karyawan pada waktu "
"tertentu atau membandingkan jumlah karyawan di berbagai periode."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:14
msgid ""
"To create a headcount report, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Reporting --> Headcount` and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat laporan jumlah karyawan, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Payroll --> Pelaporan --> Jumlah karyawan` dan klik :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:17
msgid ""
"Report name: generated automatically as `Headcount for (Company Name) on the "
"(YYYY-MM-DD)` and **cannot** be modified."
msgstr ""
"Nama laporan: dibuat secara otomatis sebagai `Jumlah karyawan untuk (Nama "
"Perusahaan) pada (YYYY-MM-DD)` dan **tidak dapat** diubah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:19
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: populated automatically (works in both single and multi-"
"company databases)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perusahaan`: terisi secara otomatis (berfungsi di database satu "
"perusahaan maupun multi-perusahaan)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:20
msgid ""
":guilabel:`From`/:guilabel:`To` dates: defaults to current date (from) and "
"blank (to). Adjust these to define the period to analyze."
msgstr ""
"Tanggal :guilabel:`Dari`/:guilabel:`Hingga`: secara default adalah tanggal "
"saat ini (dari) dan kosong (hingga). Sesuaikan ini untuk menentukan periode "
"yang akan dianalisis."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:None
msgid "A headcount report form filled out for the third quarter of 2025."
msgstr ""
"Formulir laporan jumlah karyawan yang diisi untuk kuartal ketiga tahun 2025."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:26
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Populate` to generate the report."
msgstr "Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Isi` untuk menghasilkan laporan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:28
msgid ""
"At the top of the form, a :icon:`fa-people` :guilabel:`Employees` smart "
"button appears. Clicking the button displays the total number of employees "
"for the selected period."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian atas formulir, muncul tombol pintar :icon:`fa-people` "
":guilabel:`Karyawan`. Mengklik tombol tersebut menampilkan jumlah total "
"karyawan untuk periode yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:32
msgid "View all headcount reports"
msgstr "Melihat semua laporan jumlah karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:34
msgid ""
"See how the company headcount has changed over time by viewing all headcount "
"reports in a list view."
msgstr ""
"Lihat bagaimana jumlah karyawan perusahaan telah berubah dari waktu ke waktu "
"dengan melihat semua laporan jumlah karyawan dalam tampilan daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:36
msgid ""
"To view all headcount reports, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Reporting --> Headcount`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua laporan jumlah karyawan, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Payroll --> Pelaporan --> Jumlah karyawan`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:39
msgid "View employees in a headcount"
msgstr "Melihat karyawan dalam jumlah karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:41
msgid ""
"TO get an overall view of employees and their salary impact on the company, "
"view all employee records of a specific headcount report."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mendapatkan gambaran menyeluruh tentang karyawan dan dampak gaji "
"mereka terhadap perusahaan, lihat semua catatan karyawan dari laporan jumlah "
"karyawan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:44
msgid ""
"To view the employees of a specific headcount report, click the :icon:`fa-"
"people` :guilabel:`Employees` smart button at the top of a headcount report."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat karyawan dari laporan jumlah karyawan tertentu, klik tombol "
"pintar :icon:`fa-people` :guilabel:`Karyawan` di bagian atas laporan jumlah "
"karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:47
msgid ""
"All employees from the headcount appear in a list view, grouped "
"by :guilabel:`Department`."
msgstr ""
"Semua karyawan dari jumlah karyawan muncul dalam tampilan daftar, "
"dikelompokkan berdasarkan :guilabel:`Departemen`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Employee`: the employee's full name"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Karyawan`: nama lengkap karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Department`: the department their job position is in"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Departemen`: departemen tempat posisi pekerjaan mereka berada"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:51
msgid ":guilabel:`Job Title`: their role"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jabatan`: peran mereka"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employer Cost`: how much the company pays the employee each pay-"
"period"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Biaya Pemberi Kerja`: berapa banyak perusahaan membayar karyawan "
"setiap periode pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/headcount.rst:53
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage on Payroll`: the dollar amount on payroll reports"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Upah pada Payroll`: jumlah dalam laporan payroll"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:3
msgid "Payroll analysis"
msgstr "Analisis payroll"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Payroll Analysis* report displays the total net wage for the company, "
"for the last 365 days. This report allows companies to view their payroll "
"costs and identify any trends."
msgstr ""
"Laporan *Analisis Payroll* menampilkan total upah bersih untuk perusahaan, "
"selama 365 hari terakhir. Laporan ini memungkinkan perusahaan untuk melihat "
"biaya payroll mereka dan mengidentifikasi tren apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:8
msgid ""
"To view the *Payroll Analysis* report, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Reporting --> Payroll`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat laporan *Analisis Payroll*, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --> Payroll`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:11
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Net Wage` is the default metric displayed in the report, but "
"other measures can be displayed if desired, such as *gross wage* or *days of "
"paid time off*. Click the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button "
"to view a drop-down menu of other metrics to display. Click on the desired "
"measure to display the results."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Net Wage` adalah metrik default yang ditampilkan dalam laporan, "
"tetapi ukuran lain dapat ditampilkan jika diinginkan, seperti *upah kotor* "
"atau *hari cuti berbayar*. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` untuk melihat menu drop-down metrik lain yang dapat ditampilkan. Klik "
"pada ukuran yang diinginkan untuk menampilkan hasilnya."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:None
msgid "Payroll overview report showing payroll for the last 365 days."
msgstr ""
"Laporan ringkasan payroll yang menampilkan payroll untuk 365 hari terakhir."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:22
msgid "View multiple metrics"
msgstr "Lihat beberapa metrik"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:24
msgid ""
"It is possible to view multiple metrics at one time by viewing the report in "
"the *pivot table* view. This can aid management to determine other trends, "
"such as which departments do not take time off, or which departments have "
"the highest payroll costs."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk melihat beberapa metrik sekaligus dengan melihat laporan "
"dalam tampilan *tabel pivot*. Ini dapat membantu manajemen untuk menentukan "
"tren lain, seperti departemen mana yang tidak mengambil cuti, atau "
"departemen mana yang memiliki biaya payroll tertinggi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Only one** measure is able to be displayed in the default :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`Graph` view. Multiple measures are **only** possible in "
"the :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` view."
msgstr ""
"**Hanya satu** ukuran yang dapat ditampilkan dalam tampilan :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`Graph` default. Beberapa ukuran **hanya** dimungkinkan "
"dalam tampilan :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:33
msgid ""
"To display the data in a pivot table, click on the :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` button."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan data dalam tabel pivot, klik tombol :icon:`oi-view-pivot` "
":guilabel:`Pivot`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:35
msgid ""
"The default information displayed includes the number of payslips "
"(:guilabel:`# Payslip`), the number of :guilabel:`Days of Paid Time Off` "
"and :guilabel:`Days of Unpaid Time Off`, along with the :guilabel:`Net Wage` "
"and :guilabel:`Gross Wage`. All the information is organized by department."
msgstr ""
"Informasi default yang ditampilkan mencakup jumlah slip gaji (:guilabel:`# "
"Payslip`), jumlah :guilabel:`Days of Paid Time Off` dan :guilabel:`Days of "
"Unpaid Time Off`, bersama dengan :guilabel:`Net Wage` dan :guilabel:`Gross "
"Wage`. Semua informasi diatur berdasarkan departemen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:39
msgid ""
"To display more information on the report, click "
"the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button to reveal a drop-down "
"menu. Click on any metric to display it on the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan informasi lebih lanjut pada laporan, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` untuk menampilkan menu drop-down. "
"Klik pada metrik apa pun untuk menampilkannya pada tabel pivot."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:None
msgid "Pivot table view with the various metrics on display."
msgstr "Tampilan tabel pivot dengan berbagai metrik yang ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:46
msgid "Use case: comparing payroll costs"
msgstr "Kasus penggunaan: membandingkan biaya payroll"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:48
msgid ""
"Managers can compare payroll costs, and determine which departments have "
"raised their payroll costs, either by hiring more employees, or by raising "
"salaries."
msgstr ""
"Manajer dapat membandingkan biaya payroll, dan menentukan departemen mana "
"yang telah meningkatkan biaya payroll mereka, baik dengan merekrut lebih "
"banyak karyawan, atau dengan menaikkan gaji."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:51
msgid ""
"To compare previous periods of time, first view the *Payroll Analysis* "
"report in a :ref:`pivot table <payroll_analysis/multiple>`. Then, click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(Toggle Search Panel)` icon in the "
"search bar, and click  :guilabel:`Start Date` :icon:`fa-caret-down` to "
"reveal a list of time periods (months, quarters, and years). Click on a "
"desired time period, and a :icon:`fa-adjust` :guilabel:`Comparison` section "
"appears in the search bar. Click on one of the two available options, "
"either :guilabel:`Start Date: Previous Period`, or :guilabel:`Start Date: "
"Previous Year`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membandingkan periode waktu sebelumnya, pertama lihat laporan *Payroll "
"Analysis* dalam :ref:`tabel pivot <payroll_analysis/multiple>`. Kemudian, "
"klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(Toggle Search Panel)` di bilah "
"pencarian, dan klik :guilabel:`Start Date` :icon:`fa-caret-down` untuk "
"menampilkan daftar periode waktu (bulan, kuartal, dan tahun). Klik pada "
"periode waktu yang diinginkan, dan bagian :icon:`fa-adjust` "
":guilabel:`Comparison` muncul di bilah pencarian. Klik pada salah satu dari "
"dua opsi yang tersedia, baik :guilabel:`Start Date: Previous Period`, atau "
":guilabel:`Start Date: Previous Year`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:59
msgid ""
"The report now displays three columns of information for every displayed "
"measure: a column for the current time period, a column for the previous "
"time period, and a :guilabel:`Variation` column, which displays the "
"difference between the two time periods in a color-coded percentage (green "
"for increases, red for decreases.)"
msgstr ""
"Laporan sekarang menampilkan tiga kolom informasi untuk setiap ukuran yang "
"ditampilkan: kolom untuk periode waktu saat ini, kolom untuk periode waktu "
"sebelumnya, dan kolom :guilabel:`Variation`, yang menampilkan perbedaan "
"antara dua periode waktu dalam persentase berkode warna (hijau untuk "
"kenaikan, merah untuk penurunan.)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:65
msgid ""
"In this example, the data shows an overall increase in the number of "
"payslips. Since the company pays all employees every two weeks, an increase "
"in the number of payslips (:guilabel:`# Payslips`) means that more employees "
"were hired, in this example, a 500% increase."
msgstr ""
"Dalam contoh ini, data menunjukkan peningkatan keseluruhan dalam jumlah slip "
"gaji. Karena perusahaan membayar semua karyawan setiap dua minggu, "
"peningkatan jumlah slip gaji (:guilabel:`# Payslips`) berarti lebih banyak "
"karyawan dipekerjakan, dalam contoh ini, peningkatan 500%."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:69
msgid ""
"Additionally, both the :guilabel:`Net Wage` and :guilabel:`Gross Wage` "
"increased. The department :guilabel:`RD US` showed the largest growth, with "
"both metrics increasing by approximately 350%."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, baik :guilabel:`Net Wage` maupun :guilabel:`Gross Wage` "
"meningkat. Departemen :guilabel:`RD US` menunjukkan pertumbuhan terbesar, "
"dengan kedua metrik meningkat sekitar 350%."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:0
msgid "Pivot table view comparing two years of data."
msgstr "Tampilan tabel pivot membandingkan dua tahun data."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_analysis.rst:76
msgid ":doc:`../../essentials/reporting`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../essentials/reporting`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:5
msgid "Payroll localizations"
msgstr "Lokalisasi Payroll"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:10
msgid ""
"*Payroll localizations* refer to the specific process of adapting payroll "
"systems, policies, and compliance measures to align with the specific labor "
"laws, tax regulations, and social security requirements of a particular "
"country or region."
msgstr ""
"*Lokalisasi Payroll* mengacu pada proses spesifik untuk menyesuaikan sistem "
"payroll, kebijakan, dan langkah-langkah kepatuhan agar selaras dengan undang-"
"undang ketenagakerjaan, peraturan pajak, dan persyaratan jaminan sosial "
"tertentu dari suatu negara atau wilayah."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:14
msgid ""
"This ensures that employee salaries, benefits, deductions, and contributions "
"are processed accurately and in full compliance with local legal and "
"financial obligations."
msgstr ""
"Ini memastikan bahwa gaji karyawan, tunjangan, potongan, dan kontribusi "
"diproses secara akurat dan sepenuhnya sesuai dengan kewajiban hukum dan "
"keuangan setempat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:17
msgid ""
"Localization also includes integrating country-specific payroll elements "
"such as benefits, holidays, termination rules, and reporting requirements, "
"helping businesses avoid legal risks while ensuring employees receive their "
"correct compensation."
msgstr ""
"Lokalisasi juga mencakup integrasi elemen payroll khusus negara seperti "
"tunjangan, hari libur, aturan pemutusan hubungan kerja, dan persyaratan "
"pelaporan, membantu bisnis menghindari risiko hukum sekaligus memastikan "
"karyawan menerima kompensasi yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:22
msgid "Install localization package"
msgstr "Instal paket lokalisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:24
msgid ""
"A country-specific localization module :ref:`must be installed <general/"
"install>` to properly configure and process payroll. To install the required "
"module, first open the **Apps** app."
msgstr ""
"Modul lokalisasi khusus negara :ref:`harus diinstal <general/install>` untuk "
"mengonfigurasi dan memproses payroll dengan benar. Untuk menginstal modul "
"yang diperlukan, pertama buka aplikasi **Apps**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:27
msgid ""
"Clear out the default :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`Apps` filter, then type "
"the name of the desired country into the search bar. All available modules "
"for that country are presented."
msgstr ""
"Hapus filter :guilabel:`Apps` :icon:`fa-filter` default, lalu ketik nama "
"negara yang diinginkan ke dalam bilah pencarian. Semua modul yang tersedia "
"untuk negara tersebut akan ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:31
msgid ""
"Some countries only have one localization module, while other have multiple "
"modules. This is typically when other software is neede to process payroll, "
"and importing and exporting data is required."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa negara hanya memiliki satu modul lokalisasi, sementara negara lain "
"memiliki beberapa modul. Ini biasanya terjadi ketika perangkat lunak lain "
"diperlukan untuk memproses payroll, dan impor serta ekspor data diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:35
msgid ""
"For example. when searching for **Payroll** modules for `Egypt`, the "
"following modules appear in the search, and must be installed: `Egypt - "
"Payroll` and `Egypt - Payroll with Accounting`."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, ketika mencari modul **Payroll** untuk `Mesir`, modul berikut "
"muncul dalam pencarian dan harus diinstal: `Egypt - Payroll` dan `Egypt - "
"Payroll with Accounting`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:38
msgid ""
"Refer to the :ref:`country-specific documentation <payroll_localizations/"
"countries-list>` for a complete list of the related **Payroll** modules "
"required for each specific country."
msgstr ""
"Lihat :ref:`dokumentasi khusus negara <payroll_localizations/countries-list>"
"` untuk daftar lengkap modul **Payroll** terkait yang diperlukan untuk "
"setiap negara tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:42
msgid ""
"To see if any localization modules have been installed on the database, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` page, if a localization module was installed, "
"a :guilabel:`(Country) Localization` section appears."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat apakah ada modul lokalisasi yang telah diinstal pada database, "
"navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Payroll --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`. Di halaman :guilabel:`Pengaturan`, jika modul lokalisasi "
"diinstal, bagian :guilabel:`Lokalisasi (Negara)` akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:47
msgid ""
"It is **not** recommended to alter the localization settings, unless "
"specifically required."
msgstr ""
"**Tidak** disarankan untuk mengubah pengaturan lokalisasi, kecuali secara "
"khusus diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:50
msgid ""
"Odoo can handle a multi-company configuration. This is generally done when "
"there is a main company or office location, such as a headquarters, and "
"there are other offices/branches around the country or globe, that fall "
"under that main company or headquarters. In Odoo, each company, including "
"the headquarters, must be set up as their own company/branch using the multi-"
"company method."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dapat menangani konfigurasi multi-perusahaan. Ini umumnya dilakukan "
"ketika ada perusahaan utama atau lokasi kantor, seperti kantor pusat, dan "
"ada kantor/cabang lain di seluruh negara atau dunia yang berada di bawah "
"perusahaan utama atau kantor pusat tersebut. Di Odoo, setiap perusahaan, "
"termasuk kantor pusat, harus diatur sebagai perusahaan/cabang mereka sendiri "
"menggunakan metode multi-perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:56
msgid ""
"Each individual company can have a different localization setting, since "
"locations can vary anywhere in the world, where rules and laws differ."
msgstr ""
"Setiap perusahaan individu dapat memiliki pengaturan lokalisasi yang "
"berbeda, karena lokasi dapat bervariasi di mana saja di dunia, di mana "
"aturan dan hukum berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.rst:59
msgid ""
"For more information on companies, refer to the :doc:`Companies <../../"
"general/companies>` documentation, which covers how to set up companies."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang perusahaan, lihat dokumentasi "
":doc:`Perusahaan <../../general/companies>`, yang mencakup cara mengatur "
"perusahaan."

