"**Column 2**: Specifies the percentage reduction in withholding tax, based "
"on the number of dependent children listed in Column 1, which must not be "
"exceeded to qualify for the reduction."
msgstr ""
"**Kolom 2**: Menentukan persentase pengurangan pajak pemotongan, berdasarkan "
"jumlah anak tanggungan yang tercantum di Kolom 1, yang tidak boleh dilampaui "
"untuk memenuhi syarat pengurangan."

