"eligible employees by department and / or job position."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian klik tombol **Generate Payslips**, pilih tipe struktur gaji CP200 "
"dan struktur gaji Bulan Ketiga Belas. Anda juga dapat memfilter karyawan "
"yang memenuhi syarat berdasarkan departemen dan / atau posisi pekerjaan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Double Holiday Batch Wizard."
msgstr "Wizard Batch Hari Libur Ganda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1342
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1663
