"Setelah **slip gaji** divalidasi dan dibayarkan, uang liburan sederhana yang "
"dipulihkan tercermin dalam tampilan formulir karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Holiday Pay Recovery Simple Amount."
msgstr "Jumlah Sederhana Pemulihan Uang Liburan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1792
msgid ""
"On the double holiday payslip, click :guilabel:`Compute Double Pay Recovery` "
